<p>
  A rich old man would pay a million just to be 25 again. If you are 25, you
  already own the one thing he cannot buy back: time.
</p>
<hr class="post-divider" />
<p>
  <strong>&#128293;</strong> So if you lose it all, the job, the money, the
  person, you did not lose what matters most. A wipeout is not the end, it
  is chapter one. You still have the road left to start over!
</p>
